參考書目 References
	    1. PETER V. LETSOU, CASES AND MATERIALS ON CORPORATE MERGERS AND ACQUISITIONS (Aspen Publishers, 2006).

2. SIMON M. LORNE, ACQUISITIONS AND MERGERS: NEGOTIATED AND CONTESTED TRANSACTIONS (West Group, 2001).

3. ROBERT W. HAMILTON & RICHARD A. BOOTH, BUSINESS BASICS FOR LAW STUDENTS: ESSENTIAL CONCEPTS AND APPLICATIONS (Aspen Publishers, 2006).

4. LAWRENCE E. MITCHELL, ET AL., CORPORATE FINANCE AND GOVERNANCE: CASES, MATERIALS, AND PROBLEMS FOR AN ADVANCED COURSE IN CORPORATIONS (3d. Carolina Academic Press, 2006).

5. STANLEY FOSTER REED, ET AL., THE ART OF M&A: A MERGER ACQUISITION BUYOUT GUIDE (2d. Irwin Professional, 1995).

6. BYRON E. FOX & ELEANOR M. FOX, CORPORATE ACQUISITIONS AND MERGERS (LEXIS Pub., 2004).

7. LEO HERZEL & RICHARD W. SHEPRO, BIDDERS AND TARGETS: MERGERS AND ACQUISITIONS IN THE U. S. (Basil Blackwell, 1990).

8. NORBERT HORN, CROSS-BORDER MERGERS AND ACQUISITIONS AND THE LAW (Kluwer Law International, 2001).

9. DALE A. OESTERLE, MERGERS AND ACQUISITIONS IN A NUTSHELL (2d. Thomson/West, 2006).

10. AMERICAN BAR ASSOCIATION, SECTION OF BUSINESS LAW, COMMITTEE ON NEGOTIATED ACQUISITIONS, THE M & A PROCESS: A PRACTICAL GUIDE FOR THE BUSINESS LAWYER (The Committee, 2005).

11. RICHARD A. GOLDBERG, STRUCTURING MERGERS & ACQUISITIONS (Practising Law Institute, 2001).    

